你开玩笑吧？ 怎么可以用玩具决定命运？

286
00:17:00,80 --> 00:17:02,77
It's not a toy.
这可不是玩具

287
00:17:04,33 --> 00:17:06,73
I don't know what else to do!
我别无选择

288
00:17:06,97 --> 00:17:11,24
I either keep my wife and lose one of my best friends...
不是追回老婆，失去好朋友

289
00:17:11,48 --> 00:17:15,28
...or I get divorced for the second time before I'm 30.
就是留下朋友 在30岁前离婚两次

290
00:17:15,48 --> 00:17:18,85
If anyone else has a better suggestion,let's hear it.
要是有人有更好的建议 现在就说出来

291
00:17:19,12 --> 00:17:21,45
Because I got nothing! Don't be shy.
否则我真的没有办法！ 大家别害羞

292
00:17:21,69 --> 00:17:23,95
Any suggestion will do.
各种建议都可以

293
00:17:29,46 --> 00:17:31,02
Okay,then.
好吧

294
00:17:34,26 --> 00:17:35,82
Here we go.
开始了

295
00:17:37,20 --> 00:17:38,76
Magic 8 Ball...
神奇8号球 

296
00:17:39,00 --> 00:17:41,77
...should I never see Rachel again?
我是不是不该再见瑞秋？

297
00:17:45,54 --> 00:17:46,67
"Ask Again Later."
待会再问

298
00:17:49,05 --> 00:17:51,54
Later is not good enough!
