00:21:21,99 --> 00:21:24,79
No,no,no! Leave the gloves on.
没关系，手套不用脱

361
00:21:25,53 --> 00:21:26,96
I cleaned the bathroom.
可是我刚在清厕所

362
00:21:27,20 --> 00:21:29,39
Why don't we lose the gloves.
那就脱掉吧 好

363
00:21:33,07 --> 00:21:36,06
